          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Note that 'subfigure pixels' and 'figure pixels' are the same for the parent figure, so users who want code that is usable in a subfigure can use 'subfigure pixels'."
